text: 23 Live Sex Acts (also referred to as Against Me! and the 23 Live Sex Acts) is the second live album by Against Me! It was recorded on the 2014 tour for their sixth studio album, Transgender Dysphoria Blues and released in 2015. ==Track listing== ==Personnel== *Laura Jane Grace – guitar, lead vocals *James Bowman – guitar, backing vocals *Inge Johansson – bass guitar, backing vocals *Atom Willard – drums ==References== Category:Against Me! albums Category:2015 live albums
title: 23 Live Sex Acts
